creator: RanChod Webi
descriptionHtml:
Update All App: System Updateapp is useful to update the system for android applications and update the software for new functions, features, and better performance. It is simple fast and easy to use.
It helps you to be updated with this new technology world. It helps you to update all your apps that keep up-to-date with the android version over time. It also shows the device information.
Install App: In this, you get the list of all your install Apps in your phone. In Install App you can launch any app and share the apk of the app with your friends easily. You can also see what permissions are required to run the application.
In System apps, you see a list of all system applications. In this, you get the details of the app like version of the app and install time of the application. In this also you can launch the app, share the APK and see the required permissions for the app.
In the scan app first all the applications installed in your phone are scanned and after that, you can check whether an app update is available or not.
Update All App: System Updateapp help to provide you information about your device such as OS version, API level, device name, product, version release, version incremental, SDK number of the version, a brand of your device, CPU ABI, hardware, Model name, Total ram, total internal memory size, etc.
Uninstall Apps: In the Uninstall App you can remove the app which is not in use. You can remove the app with just one click on the Uninstall.
The phone system will help you to automatically check for pending updates to all your system apps and download apps then update with just one click. After checking the update you will get the date and time of the last update check. Also, you can see the version of your device and the android security update date.
In the app usage, you can see how many times you open the app and how many hours you used the app.

Main Features:
Easy to Use.
Get installed apps updated.
Share the apk of the app.
Get the install time and version of the system app.
Get system apps updated.
Get Device info.
Update your phone software.
Uninstall user and system apps.
Auto update check gets all pending updates on one page.
Get All Pending Updates on First Click.
Check the list of permissions taken by any android apps.
Get the app open time and app use hour.
